  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>NullLogger</TypeRef> constructor creates a logger implementation that accepts the <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.ILogger">ILogger</PageRef> API but discards all messages.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[NullLogger();]]></Code>
